If you have any type of range shot, or can throw something, than do so once till you hit it. Only takes one hit, and there isn't a reason why a melee couldn't have any bow up to shoot a quick arrow or throw a knife/boulder/star. <br>
<br>
If you are a caster, use a level 1 spell. Resisted or not it is an offensive attack and will be considered such if it is resisted or not. Sometimes I would have to get my cleric faction because hw would not get it from healing my tank. To do this I used a low level stun which would always be resisted because Giants cannot be stunned, but he would get the faction hit. <br>
<br>
Stay as far away from the raid as possible. Do not get in the way. For god's sake do not start hauling off attacking &quot;Just to help&quot;. Whoever is there I am sure they can do it on their own. <br>
<br>
